# ⚙️ The Relic Registry
# This sigil binds artifacts to their lineage, governs merging, and preserves formatting rituals.

# Treat common image formats as binary relics
*.png    binary
*.jpg    binary
*.jpeg   binary
*.gif    binary

# Maintain PSD and AI source fidelity (no diffs, union merges)
*.psd    binary merge=union
*.ai     binary merge=union

# Enforce LF line endings on text scrolls
*.md     text eol=lf
*.txt    text eol=lf

# Preserve metadata integrity
*.json   text eol=lf
*.yml    text eol=lf
